text:
AWS delivers millions of leads
to hundreds of AWS Partners,

customers, and brands each year
through the AWS Sponsorship program.

This global sponsorship
is helping us to focus

on our four key areas
that we’re doing jointly with AWS:

awareness, education,
partner enablement, and demand-gen.

One of the valuable aspects
of the global partnership

is the fact that it allows us
to scale our message worldwide.

We’ve been partnering
with AWS in a variety of events.
and it’s become a priority for us

because we are seeing
more demand and awareness.

Sponsorship opportunities
include events

like re:Invent, Global Summits,
re:Inforce, Sales Kickoff,

as well as new programs
introduced each year.

I think that’s one
of the best values of AWS,
is they do both physical events

and they’re transitioning
into this digital presence.

Every AWS event
that we participate in

brings a variety of customers from
a variety of industries at all sizes.

Students all the way through
executives at fortune 500 companies.

We had a physical presence
of 250,000 users,

and we saw a 34% uplift
in our brand awareness.

AWS Sponsorships put you
face-to-face with your target customers

and enable you to showcase
your industry leadership
and knowledge.

The leads that we get from the event
are absolutely remarkable.

We’ve had nearly
350% growth year on year
in the number of leads.

It’s wonderful to be
a part of that ecosystem
and have such a strong partnership
and grow with AWS.

Join us today and grow your business
through AWS Sponsorships.
